Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.50,0:46:26.38,English,,0,0,0,,one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years,\N{\rChinese}一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.94,0:46:30.42,English,,0,0,0,,one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years, one hundred years,\N{\rChinese}一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年，一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.56,0:46:33.32,English,,0,0,0,,one hundred years, one hundred years,\N{\rChinese}一百年，一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.42,0:46:35.98,English,,0,0,0,,one hundred years, one hundred years,\N{\rChinese}一百年，一百年，
