Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.20,0:46:42.08,English,,0,0,0,,the horse is able to travel as fast as light itself\N{\rChinese}这匹马能像光一样快地行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.08,0:46:45.12,English,,0,0,0,,and so the builders able to really quickly build\N{\rChinese}于是建筑师们能够迅速建造
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.12,0:46:46.30,English,,0,0,0,,that wall and\N{\rChinese}那堵墙和
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:49.14,English,,0,0,0,,he's about to finish the wall Odin says\N{\rChinese}他正要完成墙，奥丁说
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.14,0:46:53.00,English,,0,0,0,,Loki you got us in you got us into this mess\N{\rChinese}洛基，你把我们拖进这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.00,0:46:56.18,English,,0,0,0,,get us out of this mess or I will kill you so\N{\rChinese}把我们拉出来，否则我就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.18,0:46:58.58,English,,0,0,0,,what does Loki do Loki thinks and\N{\rChinese}洛基做了什么？洛基在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.58,0:47:01.14,English,,0,0,0,,he's a shapeshifter right and\N{\rChinese}他是个变形者，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.14,0:47:05.10,English,,0,0,0,,he's able to shape shapeshift into\N{\rChinese}他能变身成……
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.10,0:47:10.58,English,,0,0,0,,a mirror a beautiful horse okay like this the birds horse sees the mirror\N{\rChinese}一面镜子，一匹漂亮的马，好的，就像这样，鸟马看到镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.58,0:47:14.14,English,,0,0,0,,and becomes really excited right\N{\rChinese}并且变得非常兴奋，对吧？
