Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.28,0:47:24.36,English,,0,0,0,,and Loki gives birth to a horse a baby horse\N{\rChinese}洛基诞生了一匹小马
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.36,0:47:27.60,English,,0,0,0,,that then becomes Odin's horse okay that's\N{\rChinese}那时它变成了奥丁的马，好吧那是……
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.60,0:47:31.08,English,,0,0,0,,idea of resourcefulness there are\N{\rChinese}资源的灵活性概念在此
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.08,0:47:33.88,English,,0,0,0,,some really funny stories you can read about the story of Odin and\N{\rChinese}有一些非常有趣的故事，你可以在北欧神话的故事书中读到关于奥丁和洛基的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.88,0:47:35.92,English,,0,0,0,,Loki in the book of the stories within Norse mythology\N{\rChinese}在北欧神话的故事书中，关于奥丁和洛基的故事有很多有趣的章节
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.92,0:47:37.86,English,,0,0,0,,okay one of the funniest is this\N{\rChinese}好的，最有趣的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.86,0:47:43.44,English,,0,0,0,,Thor has a magic hammer named Mjolnir he loves it he loves it\N{\rChinese}索尔有一把名为Mjolnir的魔杵，他很爱它，爱得把它放在枕头下，某天醒来却发现它不见了。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.44,0:47:47.50,English,,0,0,0,,so much that he sleeps with it he puts it under his pillow one day he wakes up\N{\rChinese}索尔有一把名为Mjolnir的魔杵，他很爱它，爱得把它放在枕头下，某天醒来却发现它不见了。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.50,0:47:50.56,English,,0,0,0,,and finds it missing so\N{\rChinese}索尔有一把名为Mjolnir的魔杵，他很爱它，爱得把它放在枕头下，某天醒来却发现它不见了。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.56,0:47:53.26,English,,0,0,0,,of course he thinks it must be Loki because\N{\rChinese}当然，他认为一定是洛基，因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.26,0:47:55.90,English,,0,0,0,,Loki's always playing these tricks on the gods but\N{\rChinese}洛基总是在神们面前玩这些把戏，但……
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.90,0:47:58.92,English,,0,0,0,,Loki says I didn't do it and I'll find out for you who\N{\rChinese}洛基说：我没干，我会替你查清楚的。
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.92,0:48:01.88,English,,0,0,0,,did it so Loki explores and he finds out\N{\rChinese}他做了这件事，洛基去探查，发现是法萨因国王偷走了锤子。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.88,0:48:05.18,English,,0,0,0,,that it was the Farsain king who\N{\rChinese}法萨因国王才是那位偷走锤子的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.18,0:48:08.46,English,,0,0,0,,stole the hammer the Farsain king will only\N{\rChinese}法萨因国王才是那位偷走锤子的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.46,0:48:10.58,English,,0,0,0,,return the hammer if the\N{\rChinese}把锤子还给他
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.58,0:48:12.84,English,,0,0,0,,gods give him Freyja\N{\rChinese}神们给他弗雷雅作妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.84,0:48:17.32,English,,0,0,0,,as a wife Loki goes back\N{\rChinese}洛基又回去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.32,0:48:20.80,English,,0,0,0,,and Freyja says screw off I'm not I'm not going to do this\N{\rChinese}并且弗雷雅说：好了，去吧，我不去做这事。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.80,0:48:21.72,English,,0,0,0,,so\N{\rChinese}于是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.72,0:48:24.50,English,,0,0,0,,Loki says to Thor I have a plan the\N{\rChinese}洛基对托尔说：我有个计划。
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.50,0:48:28.00,English,,0,0,0,,plan is he's going to dress Thor up as\N{\rChinese}计划是他要把托尔打扮成弗雷雅
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.00,0:48:32.66,English,,0,0,0,,Freyja he's going to put a wedding dress and a veil on\N{\rChinese}他要给托尔穿上婚纱和面纱
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.74,0:48:35.22,English,,0,0,0,,Thor and\N{\rChinese}托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.22,0:48:41.16,English,,0,0,0,,Loki will disguise himself as a bridesmaid okay stupid plan\N{\rChinese}洛基会伪装成新娘的侍女，好的，愚蠢的计划
