Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.78,0:49:06.44,English,,0,0,0,,is eating this oxen he's drinking all this beer he's burping in the process\N{\rChinese}托尔正在吃着这头牛，他喝着啤酒，咕噜咕噜地打嗝
